            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13980553/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13980553/" class="">第274页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45574755/" class=" " title="满月雕弓">满月雕弓</a>
                (一沙一世界，一花一天堂。)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13980553">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">清 赵翼“少时学语苦难圆，只道工夫半未全。到老方知非力取，三分人事七分天。”</span>
